>\n</div>\n</div>\n<hr/>\n<div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<nav class=\"gcweb-menu\" typeof=\"SiteNavigationElement\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Menu</h2>\n<button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Main </span>Menu <span class=\"expicon glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down\"></span></button>\n<ul aria-orientation=\"vertical\" data-ajax-replace=\"/content/dam/canada/sitemenu/sitemenu-v2-en.html\" role=\"menu\">\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/jobs.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Jobs and the workplace</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Travel and tourism</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/business.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Business and industry</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/benefits.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Benefits</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/health.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Health</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/taxes.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Taxes</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/environment.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Environment and natural resources</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/defence.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">National security and defence</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/culture.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/policing.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadians.html\">Immigration and citizenship for Canadians</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadians/adopt-child-abroad.html\">Adopt a child from abroad</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<h1 dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">\nAdoption authorities contacts</h1>\n<div><div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<span class=\"wb-toggle\" data-toggle='{\"selector\": \"main summary\", \"print\": \"on\"}'></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\" id=\"push-message\">Features</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<p>Find the various contacts if you want to adopt a child from abroad.</p>\n<h2>Government of Canada (federal)</h2>\n<p>The federal government is only responsible for the immigration or citizenship process of an adopted child.</p>\n<p>Under the <a href=\"http://www.ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?qnum=1183&amp;top=2\">Hague Convention</a>, Canada’s federal central authority is Intercountry Adoption Services, which is part of Immigration, Refugees and Citizenship Canada.</p>\n<details>\n<summary>The role of Intercountry Adoption Services</summary>\n<p>The role of Intercountry Adoption Services is to</p>\n<ul>\n<li>collect and distribute <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadians/adopt-child-abroad/processes.html#Adoption_information\">adoption information</a> to\n\t\t\t<ul>\n<li>Canadian provincial and territorial central authorities</li>\n<li>foreign authorities</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>help with communication, cooperation and coordination\n\t\t\t<ul>\n<li>between federal and provincial and territorial central authorities</li>\n<li>within the federal government</li>\n<li>with foreign central authorities or adoption authorities</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>help to address issues such as <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadians/adopt-child-abroad/caution.html\">unethical and irregular adoption practices</a></li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<p>Immigration, Refugees and Citizenship Canada<br/>\nIntercountry Adoption Services<br/>\nFamily and Social Immigration<br/><a href=\"mailto:IA-Inquiries@cic.gc.ca\">IA-Inquiries@cic.gc.ca</a></p>\n<h2>Provincial and territorial central adoption authorities</h2>\n<p>The <strong>provinces or territories</strong> are responsible for the <strong>adoption</strong> process.</p>\n<!-- FIELDFLOW starts here  -->\n<div class=\"wb-fieldflow\" data-wb-fieldflow='{\n\t\"hideelm\": \".result\",\n\t\"live\" : true,\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\"reset\": { \"action\": \"addClass\", \"source\":\".result\", \"class\": \"hidden\" }\n}'>\n<p>Choose a province or territory to find its central adoption authority</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#al\"}'><a href=\"#al\">Alberta</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#bc\"}'><a href=\"#bc\">British Columbia</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#mb\"}'><a href=\"#mb\">Manitoba</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#nb\"}'><a href=\"#nb\">New Brunswick</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#nl\"}'><a href=\"#nl\">Newfoundland and Labrador</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#ns\"}'><a href=\"#ns\">Nova Scotia</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#nt\"}'><a href=\"#nt\">Northwest Territories</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#nv\"}'><a href=\"#nv\">Nunavut</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#on\"}'><a href=\"#on\">Ontario</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#pe\"}'><a href=\"#pe\">Prince Edward Island</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#qc\"}'><a href=\"#qc\">Quebec</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#sk\"}'><a href=\"#sk\">Saskatchewan</a></li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\", \"class\": \"hidden\",\"source\": \"#yk\"}'><a href=\"#yk\">Yukon</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"al\">\n<p><strong>Alberta</strong> – Alberta Adoption Services, <a href=\"https://www.alberta.ca/international-adoption\" rel=\"external\">Ministry of Children’s Services</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"bc\">\n<p><strong>British Columbia</strong> – Adoption, <a href=\"https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/life-events/birth-adoption/adoptions/how-to-adopt-a-child/adopt-from-another-country\" rel=\"external\">Ministry of Children and Family Development</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"mb\">\n<p><strong>Manitoba</strong> – Child Protection Branch, <a href=\"https://www.gov.mb.ca/fs/childfam/intercountry_adoption.html\" rel=\"external\">Department of Families</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"nb\">\n<p><strong>New Brunswick</strong> – Child &amp; Youth Services Branch, <a href=\"https://socialsupportsnb.ca/en/program/adopting-child-or-youth\" rel=\"external\">Department of Social Development</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"nl\">\n<p><strong>Newfoundland and Labrador</strong> – Adoption Services, <a href=\"https://www.gov.nl.ca/cssd/adoption/#application\" rel=\"external\">Department of Children, Seniors and Social Development</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"ns\">\n<p><strong>Nova Scotia</strong> – Adoption Services, <a href=\"https://novascotia.ca/coms/families/adoption/InternationalAdoption.html\" rel=\"external\">Department of Community Services</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"nt\">\n<p><strong>Northwest Territories</strong> – Adoption, <a href=\"https://www.hss.gov.nt.ca/en/services/adoption\" rel=\"external\">Department of Health and Social Services</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"nv\">\n<p><strong>Nunavut</strong> – <a href=\"https://www.gov.nu.ca/family-services/information/adoption\" rel=\"external\">Department of Family Services</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"on\">\n<p><strong>Ontario</strong> – Adoption, <a href=\"https://www.ontario.ca/page/international-adoptions-ontario\" rel=\"external\">Ministry of Children, Community and Social Services</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"pe\">\n<p><strong>Prince Edward Island</strong> – Adoption, <a href=\"https://www.princeedwardisland.ca/en/information/family-and-human-services/adoption\" rel=\"external\">Department of Social Development and Housing</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"qc\">\n<p><strong>Quebec</strong> – Secrétariat aux services internationaux à l’enfant, <a href=\"https://www.quebec.ca/en/family-and-support-for-individuals/pregnancy-parenthood/adoption/international-adoption\" rel=\"external\">Ministère de la Santé et des Services sociaux</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"sk\">\n<p><strong>Saskatchewan</strong> – Adoption, <a href=\"https://www.saskatchewan.ca/residents/births-deaths-marriages-and-divorces/births-and-adoptions/adoption/planning-to-adopt#further-information\" rel=\"external\">Ministry of Social Services</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result\" id=\"yk\">\n<p><strong>Yukon</strong> – Adoption Services, <a href=\"https://yukon.ca/en/legal-and-social-supports/childrens-services/find-out-about-adopting-child\" rel=\"external\">Government of Yukon Children’s Services</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2025-02-21\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-footer\">\n<footer id=\"wb-info\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">About this site</h2>\n<div class=\"gc-contextual\"><div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Immigration and citizenship</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/results-by-topic.asp?top=2\">Help Centre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/contact-ircc.htm